  "content": "\n \n \n  <p data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\"><br><br style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n  <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-id=\"Mzg3MzUxOTkyNQ==\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/BJFBu9NXhBDLDYZTsNck9vYlXjGJgCQEdfxl0Hoc9TI8652DJuiaODDicJfg7KsSatvYqFAyKUPNxBrdSYh6DH6g/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-nickname=\"勤商日历\" data-alias=\"qinshangrili\" data-signature=\"勤商日历，是一款专门为个人成长开发的，通过“制定目标，每周复盘，制定计划”，以天为单位，学习一个商业小知识；以周为单位，不断复盘，不断练习，不断提升自己。每年十月下旬开售，欢迎关注~\" data-from=\"0\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\"></mp-common-profile>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-backh=\"579\" data-backw=\"578\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"579\" data-ratio=\"1.000925925925926\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6be244a8-65e1-4a47-c550-9ba9504b3e00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6be244a8-65e1-4a47-c550-9ba9504b3e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"white-space: normal;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 677px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;width: 677px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;width: 677px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <section style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-size-adjust: inherit;text-align: start;line-height: 25.6px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      <section style=\"margin-right: 0em;margin-left: 0em;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-size-adjust: inherit;line-height: 25.6px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <section style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 0.5em;margin-left: 0.5em;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-size: medium;text-align: center;line-height: 1.5em;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 13px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">观点 / 刘润&nbsp; &nbsp; 主笔&nbsp;<span style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;\">/ </span><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:13px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;\">方雁橙&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;责编&nbsp;/ 黄静</span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 20px;margin-left: 16px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.5em;text-align: right;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <em style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: start;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(165, 165, 165);visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: right;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(95, 95, 95);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: start;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(165, 165, 165);visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">本文首发于2022年1</em></span><em style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: start;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">月</em></strong></em>\n    <br style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   </section>\n   <hr style=\"outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;border-style: solid;border-right-width: 0px;border-bottom-width: 0px;border-left-width: 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"122\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"122\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504248037\" data-ratio=\"0.22314814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/93d5d956-351e-49eb-3b42-92d460571600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;color:rgb(95, 95, 95);visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.578px;width:100%;font-size:15px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;height:auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/93d5d956-351e-49eb-3b42-92d460571600/public\">今天，我们重发一篇过往比较受欢迎的文章《<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjM5MjQ4MQ==&amp;mid=2651665964&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=141e23911358d5daa9ef0cbfcc238022&amp;chksm=bd106d628a67e474262d48446705090ead84df438c8fa9bc48501d310e9c57534e2fc62b569e&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" data-linktype=\"2\">做难而正确的事情</a>》，希望对你有所启发。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">以下是这篇重发文章正文。</span></p>\n  <p><br></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">今天，我们来聊一个话题，应该选择简单的事情，还是难的事情。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:start;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"35\" data-backw=\"546\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504248038\" data-ratio=\"0.06388888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edaae7a2-2568-46fb-e6ad-fa2327218100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-wrap: wrap;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edaae7a2-2568-46fb-e6ad-fa2327218100/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"57\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"80\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504279176\" data-ratio=\"0.10462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f37ac9d2-dddf-4c61-32a3-80db84d04c00/public\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f37ac9d2-dddf-4c61-32a3-80db84d04c00/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.544px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-size:20px;\">先做简单的事，还是难的事</span></strong></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\"><br>\n     前段时间，有同学问了一个问题，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我要不要先做一点简单的事情，挣到钱之后，再做难的事情。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">为什么一开始就要做那么难的事情，比如去招标。万一失败怎么办？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">我的看法是这样的。如果你去做一件事，失败了。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">说明你前面没有做难的事情，没有构建自己的核心竞争力。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">因为真正难的不是招标失败，失败并不难。难的是什么，难的是你之前做了很多事情，给自己挖了一条护城河。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，你一开始和一个科学家合作，研究了三年五年，研发出一种药物配方。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这个过程是很难的，一旦做出来之后，找到合作对象这个事情就变得简单了。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，你一开始花了很长时间去开发一款软件，特别难。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">开发了一年多，终于开发出来了，这时候后面的事情就变得非常容易了。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">那一开始先做点简单的事情，先挣点钱。有没有道理呢？也有道理。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但简单的事情挣钱，可能是你抓住了红利，你进入了一个行业，赶上了红利，发现挣钱很容易。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果看到了红利，赶上了红利，当然要抓住。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">但你心里要知道，你挣的是红利的钱，但红利是会消失的。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">所以你还是要去做难而正确的事情，要去积蓄力量，要去建设品牌，要去挖护城河，要去构建你的核心竞争力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这样未来红利消失之后，大家都觉得挣钱越来越难了，你还能挣到钱。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这就跟减肥一样，有个人已经高血脂了，营养师告诉他，你要规律饮食，要多吃清淡的食物。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">但这个人喜欢重口味，怎么办？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">算了，想吃啥吃啥，这件事很简单。但你要贪图一时口腹之欲，就要以健康为代价。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">等你真正意识到问题严重性的时候，这件事就会变得非常难。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果你坚持规律饮食，吃清淡的东西，这件事一开始很难。但你会越来越健康，它给你带来的价值是巨大的。<br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"35\" data-backw=\"546\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504248039\" data-ratio=\"0.06388888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edaae7a2-2568-46fb-e6ad-fa2327218100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-wrap: wrap;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edaae7a2-2568-46fb-e6ad-fa2327218100/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: center;color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"57\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"80\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504279177\" data-ratio=\"0.10462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6e04703-3332-4d1a-cdc7-a0cbd583c700/public\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6e04703-3332-4d1a-cdc7-a0cbd583c700/public\"></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;text-indent:0em;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 0em;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-size:20px;\">进窄门，走远路，见微光</span></strong><br></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\"><br>\n     这也是我们经常说的</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">进窄门，走远路，见微光。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">什么意思呢。就是你只有选择更难走的路，做更难的事情，才更有可能走得远，才更有可能看到更好的风光。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">余华的小说《兄弟》的后记中有一段话：</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“写作就是这样奇妙，从狭窄开始往往写出宽广，从宽广开始反而写出狭窄。”</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">创业也是这样，如果你选择的是一条看起来非常宽广，完全没有门槛的路，常常会走投无路。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果你选择了一条狭窄的，看起来很难走的路，越到后面，可能越开阔，越宽广。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">因为很多事情，一开始很难做，很多人一看就想，算了，我不干了，于是就转身离开了。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这时候，只有你坚持下来了。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">然后你发现，后面的路越来越宽，越来越宽，风光秀丽，鸟语花香。在这条路上，跟你竞争的人也越来越少，越来越少。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，你想进入咨询行业，你很纠结，是选管理咨询，还是战略咨询。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果选择管理咨询，开始相对容易点，但越到后面，在这个赛道上，跟你竞争的人就越多。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">选择战略咨询，一开始很难，门槛比较高。但进入这个赛道后，你的路就会越走越宽。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">窄门，开始非常难。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">一旦你进入，你就会发现，里面非常宽敞，能和你竞争的人非常少。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">宽门，一开始容易进。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">但之后，会有大量的人涌进来，越往里走，人越多，路越窄，越难走。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">最后会出现一种什么情况呢？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">大量的人挤在一条狭窄的、崎岖的小路上，下面可能是万丈深渊，有人已经掉下去了，有人等着更多的人掉下去。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">竞争非常惨烈，但大家都不愿意往回走。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么？因为沉没成本。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">我都跑了这么久了，往回走就意味着前功尽弃，拼了命也要挤过去啊。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">怎么办，先把车卖了，还不行，把房卖了。因为卖了车和房，增加了沉没成本。无论如何也要把本钱挣回来。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">所以就拼命挤，拼命挤，拼命挤，很痛苦，但是不敢停下来。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">停下来，就意味着血本无归。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">所以，但凡一开始非常容易，门槛非常低的事情，越到后面可能就越不容易。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">因为没有限制，谁都可以进去，进去的人越多，竞争就越激烈，路就越窄。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"35\" data-backw=\"546\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504248040\" data-ratio=\"0.06388888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edaae7a2-2568-46fb-e6ad-fa2327218100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-wrap: wrap;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/edaae7a2-2568-46fb-e6ad-fa2327218100/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:center;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"57\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"80\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504279178\" data-ratio=\"0.10462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ad77c1f-8d9c-4aa9-4875-70fa6b33b600/public\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9ad77c1f-8d9c-4aa9-4875-70fa6b33b600/public\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:16px;text-align:start;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);text-indent: 0em;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: justify;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-size:20px;\">做难而正确的事</span></strong><br></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\"><br>\n     怎么办？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">分享两点思考。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1）坚持做难而正确的事情。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“要进窄门，不要进宽门。宽门易进，所以人多，但必至灭亡，窄门里人少，方得永生。”这句话同样适用于创业。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果想让后面的路走得更容易一些，你一开始可能要做点难的事情。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，你是做电商的，看到大家都刷单，你要不要刷单呢？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">选择刷单这件事很简单，真正难的是什么？是你对价值观的坚守，坚持不刷单。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这件事非常难，因为同行都这么做，平台也把这种行为合理化了。你不刷单，意味着你要牺牲一部分利润。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">越到后面，行业越来越规范，刷单这种混乱的现象就会被整治，熬过了混乱期，那些坚持不刷单，诚信经营的卖家，路会越走越宽。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，你是一家创业公司的CEO，事事都亲力亲为。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">慢慢地，你成了公司发展的瓶颈，因为整个公司都是能力不如你的人。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这会导致一种什么后果呢，限制公司成长，公司成长速度很难超出你的技能范围。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这时候最重要的事情是什么，是你做出改变。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">做出改变很难。但你只有做出改变，引进更优秀的职业经理人，公司才能继续成长。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2）找到宽门里的窄门。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果一开始选择了一件简单的事情，进的是宽门，怎么办。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">找到宽门里的窄门。什么意思呢，就是你要在宽门里找到一条看起来更难走，更少人走的路。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这样后面路越来越窄，越来越难走的时候，你就可以错开竞争。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当所有人都在热热闹闹往前走的时候，你要去构建自己的核心竞争力，修炼一项技能，打造一身铠甲。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">这样路越来越窄，竞争越来越激烈，大家拼命往前挤的时候，你的优势就会凸现出来。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，开餐厅这件事。开餐厅这件事一开始很容易，门槛很低。所以进入的人很多。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">慢慢地，随着越来越多人进入，你发现越往后越难，竞争越来越激烈。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">怎么办？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">找到宽门里的窄门，构建核心竞争力。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">比如，在整个火锅行业还不重视服务的时候，海底捞就通过极致的服务，构建起了核心竞争力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">后面进入火锅行业的人越来越多，火锅店也越来越多。但很多人一提到吃火锅，还是会第一时间想到海底捞。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">比如，短视频兴起后，很多人抓住了这波红利。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">刚开始进入这个赛道的人比较少，供小于求。很多质量一般的短视频博主也赚到了钱。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">随后，哗啦啦，这个赛道挤满了人，竞争越来越激烈。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这时候，那些选择做难的事情，认真打磨内容，专注构建自己核心能力的人，就会有更多机会。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">因为平台开始扶持认真做内容的博主，让优质的内容有更多曝光的机会。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">而那些一直呆在宽门里的人，慢慢就被推到了窄路上，稍不留神，就有掉下赛道的风险。<br></span>\n  </section>\n  <h4 style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:16px;margin-right:16px;text-align:start;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"34\" data-backw=\"546\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504248042\" data-ratio=\"0.06296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6c1f2bc6-df64-4afe-d29d-40f83c984500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6c1f2bc6-df64-4afe-d29d-40f83c984500/public\"></h4>\n  <h1 style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin-left:16px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:16px;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"58\" data-backw=\"546\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"56\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"504279179\" data-ratio=\"0.10648148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b212d037-b809-405a-36c2-54aa3a807400/public\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b212d037-b809-405a-36c2-54aa3a807400/public\"></span></h1>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 82, 255);outline:0px;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 82, 255);outline:0px;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:24px;\"></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 24px;\"></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">进窄门，走远路，见微光。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">就像文章里提到的，</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“写作就是这样奇妙，从狭窄开始往往写出宽广，从宽广开始反而写出狭窄。”</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">创业也是这样，如果你选择的是一条看起来非常宽广，完全没有门槛的路，常常会走投无路。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">你只有在一开始选择难走的路，才有可能避开拥挤的人群，见到更好的风光。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">如果开始进的是宽门，怎么办。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">找到宽门里的窄门，看见同行看不见，看不起，看不懂的机会。即使红利消失了，你依旧能走得久，也走得远。</span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 16px;white-space: normal;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(76, 76, 76);\">共勉。</span></section><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:start;\"><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:medium;line-height:1.5em;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:center;\">\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "在不确定的商业环境中，选择难而正确的事，进窄门走远路，构建长期竞争力是关键。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "在不确定的商业环境中，选择难而正确的事，进窄门走远路，构建长期竞争力是关键。",
